text: @redsparrowsg provides a feast for the senses! Indulge your sense of sight admiring the intricately plated dishes. Indulge your sense of smell from the whiff of spices and flavours. Indulge your sense of touch as the warm fragrant steam caresses your face. Indulge your sense of sound with the familial family chatter.
